Client Requirement Document
Project Name: TALEEM GYM – Admin Dashboard (PWA)
Prepared For: Gym Owner / Admin
Platform: Progressive Web App (PWA)
Version: 1.0 (MVP Scope)
1.  Project Objective
To develop a mobile-friendly admin dashboard that enables gym owners to manage members, track
attendance, and handle both offline and online payments efficiently.
2.  Platform Overview
The system will be a Progressive Web App (PWA):
• Accessible via browser
• Installable on mobile devices
• Optimized for Android usage
• Fast loading with basic offline support
3.  Core Functional Requirements
3.1 Dashboard Overview
The dashboard will display:
• Total active members
• Expired memberships
• Daily attendance count
• Revenue summary (online + offline combined)
3.2 Member Management
Admin can:
• Add new members
• Edit member details
• View member list
Each member includes:
• Name
• Phone number
• Membership plan
• Start & expiry date
• Status (Active / Expired)
3.3 Attendance Management
• Mark daily attendance
• View attendance logs
• Track individual attendance history
3.4 Membership Plans
• Create plans (Monthly, Quarterly, etc.)
• Assign plans to members
• Track validity and expiry
3.5 Payment Management
3.5.1 Offline Payments
• Record manual payments (cash/UPI/etc.)
• View payment history
3.5.2 Online Payment Integration
The system will support online payment collection with:
• Payment link or in-app payment option
• Integration with a payment gateway (e.g., Razorpay / Stripe)
• Automatic payment status updates (Success / Failed / Pending)
• Payment records linked to members
3.6 Notifications & Alerts
• Membership expiry reminders
• Payment status alerts
• Dashboard notifications for key actions
4.  Security Requirements
• Secure admin authentication
• Secure payment processing via trusted gateway
• No storage of sensitive card/payment details on system
5.  User Interface & Experience
• Clean, minimal interface
• Mobile-first design
• Easy navigation
• Fast interaction for daily usage
6.  Performance Requirements
• Load time under 3 seconds
• Smooth performance on standard Android devices
• Reliable payment status updates
7.  Excluded Features
• Member enquiry system
• Staff management
• Advanced analytics
8.  Deliverables
• Functional PWA (installable)
• Admin dashboard with all listed features
• Payment gateway integration
• Backend + database setup
• Deployment-ready system
9.  Future Enhancements
• Member mobile app
• Advanced financial reports
• Multi-admin roles
10.  Approval
This document defines the scope of the initial version.
Additional features will be treated as future upgrades.
